## OmvFeatureFilterDescriptionBuilder.OmvFeatureFilterDescriptionBuilderOptions.processPointsDefault property

If `true`<!-- -->, all unspecified point features will be processed. If `false`<!-- -->, all unspecified point features will be ignored.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
processPointsDefault?: boolean;
```
